title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Fast-paced changes can create a lot of mental fog today. Of course, it makes perfect sense to obtain a better picture of what is going on near the center of the action before choosing if you want to venture into the thick of it. For example, it may be a smart strategy to temporarily position yourself as an observer and simply watch developments unfold while determining how to proceed. Others envy your powers of observation, and your shrewd approach to decision-making. Listen to sharp instincts that advise looking before you leap. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
